{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg"},"name":"河井武士","relation":"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/96/fa/4232_prsn_bBAP2.jpg?r=1675677585","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/96/fa/4232_prsn_bBAP2.jpg?r=1675677585","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/96/fa/4232_prsn_bBAP2.jpg?r=1675677585","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/96/fa/4232_prsn_bBAP2.jpg?r=1675677585"},"name":"神谷浩史","short_summary":"高中时期是理科生，加入青二塾以前只是一般地看着动画，没有想要成为声优的念头。高三时，于7月份加入同年级朋友组建的演剧团，在9月份的地区演剧大赛中意外获得“个人演技奖”，自此开始对演剧事业产生兴趣。想考艺术类大学所以在高三理转文，并不成功，高考落榜。\r\n另寻出路的时候在杂志上看到了青二塾的广告，征得父母同意考上其东京校第14期。当时不了解其实这里培养的是声优而不是演员，起初产生了“别干了”的消极情绪，但之后仍在青二塾坚持学习了下去，不过是“不良墅生”，同学和老师之后都笑称当时他“很狂妄”，并不参加到同学间的自主练习中。1994年，19岁的神谷从青二塾毕业，顺利加入青二事务所。\r\n出道的头几年，相比于同期甚至后期的声优们很快的大放异彩，神谷则是全部出演酱油的路人角色。2006年8月7日，因为遭逢交通事故而住院治疗。虽然经纪公司并不愿透漏事故的原因，但从关系人口中得知似乎是骑乘机车时发生的。车祸似乎是神谷事业的一个拐点。2007年因担任《再见!绝望先生》、《高达00》等作品主角的CV而受到瞩目，之后在《夏目友人帐》、《化物语》等作品中为主角配音获得极高人气，目前则是因为饰演《进击的巨人》中的里维兵长而再度爆红。\r\n\r\n2025年1月1日，宣布与女演员、模特逢泽莉娜结婚。1月4日，在广播节目中透露自己于8年前起单身，后因此节目而与逢泽莉娜结缘，大约2年前开始交往。","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4232,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":10734},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/70/d8/28115_crt_vL10O.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/70/d8/28115_crt_vL10O.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/70/d8/28115_crt_vL10O.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/70/d8/28115_crt_vL10O.jpg"},"name":"アナウンス","relation":"客串","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/56/40/23832_prsn_Qp9PB.jpg?r=1464934989","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/56/40/23832_prsn_Qp9PB.jpg?r=1464934989","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/56/40/23832_prsn_Qp9PB.jpg?r=1464934989","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/56/40/23832_prsn_Qp9PB.jpg?r=1464934989"},"name":"河内孝博","short_summary":"日本の男性声優、ナレーター、修斗オフィシャルリング・アナウンサー兼テレビ実況担当。\r\n富山県氷見市出身。青二プロダクション所属。日本芸術専門学校講師。","career":["seiyu"],"id":23832,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":28115},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/5b/fb/174881_crt_ngnOE.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5b/fb/174881_crt_ngnOE.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/5b/fb/174881_crt_ngnOE.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/5b/fb/174881_crt_ngnOE.jpg"},"name":"高嶺竜児","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/44/f6/4716_prsn_M5yir.jpg?r=1735749673"},"name":"森田成一","short_summary":"日本の声優、俳優、ナレーターである。血液型はA型。\r\n特技  剣道、空手\r\n趣味  写真撮影、クラシックカメラ収集、各種モノ作り\r\n\r\n芸歴\r\n2003年　青二プロダクション\r\n2021年　フリー\r\n2025年　ステイラック","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":4716,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":174881}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":5,"gender":"male","birth_day":23,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/9e/01/10734_crt_BMi72.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"河井武士","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"河井武士"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"纯假名","v":"かわいたけし"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"},{"key":"生日","value":"5月23日"},{"key":"身高","value":"163cm"},{"key":"体重","value":"49kg"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":10734,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":6,"gender":"male","birth_day":29,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/5b/f